  <brief_title>Intraoperative Floppy Iris Syndrome in Korean Patients Taking α1-Adrenergic Receptor Antagonists</brief_title>
  <official_title>Intraoperative Floppy Iris Syndrome in Korean Patients Taking α1-Adrenergic Receptor Antagonists</official_title>
